arguments.template:
<ion-app>
  <ion-split-pane contentId="AO_APP_CONTENT" [when]="ao.menu.stacked()">

    <ion-menu menuId="AO_APP_MENU" contentId="AO_APP_CONTENT" type="overlay">
      <ion-header>

        <ng-content select="[slot=header]"></ng-content>

      </ion-header>
      <ion-content>

        <ng-content select="[slot=menu]"></ng-content>

      </ion-content>
      <ion-header>

        <ng-content select="[slot=footer]"></ng-content>

      </ion-header>
    </ion-menu>

    <ion-router-outlet id="AO_APP_CONTENT"></ion-router-outlet>

  </ion-split-pane>
</ion-app>
